    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "translated": "You have more power to move those around you than you realize."
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "translated": "And you have the kindness to support others, too."
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "translated": "Indeed."
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "translated": "Margarete says it often as well."
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "translated": "\"I can't let myself be outdone by Mei-senpai.\""
    },
    {
